Value.value: Always glad to see fresh faces!

Listen closely, all of you. I am Gabriel and I am in charge of this camp. There is a storm that lurks below. The gibberlings, mindless vicious creatures driven by hunger and chaos, have taken hold. Their numbers need to be reduced and that is where you come in. If you have come alone there are others across the way waiting to join you. Get yourself a companion and continue downwards. Be warned though we never quite know what we expect down below... Good luck!
